data.enText: a chemical element. Platinum is a silver-grey precious metal , used in making expensive jewellery and in industry.

tr: occurs in some nickel and copper ores and is also found native in some deposits

value.def: Platinum is a very valuable, silvery-grey metal. It is often used for making jewellery.
Platinum hair is very fair, almost white.

example.ex: ...a platinum blonde with thick eye shadow and scarlet lipstick.
example.tran: 涂着浓浓眼影和鲜红唇膏的银灰色头发的女子

trans: (给唱片销售量极高的歌手等颁发的)白金唱片
